<p><b>Benefits:</b></p>
<p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-40440 aligncenter" title="Fire and Hazard Detection" src="https://www.invertio.in/blog/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/7.jpg.webp" alt="Fire and Hazard Detection" width="1200" height="336" /></p>
